N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 200.13 - Impaneling of grand juries

State Regulations

There shall be a grand jury drawn and
impaneled for such terms of a superior court as may be provided on the annual
schedule of terms established by the Chief Administrator of the Courts. Whenever the public interest requires, additional grand juries may be drawn and
impaneled as authorized by the Chief Administrator. Notes
